config MTK_BMA253
	bool "MTK_BMA53 for MediaTek package"
	default n
	help
	  It support different accelerometer sensor.
          If this option is set,
	  it will support
          MTK_BMA253 Accelerometer.

config BMA253_LOWPASS
	bool "MTK_BMA253 for Mediatek package"
	default n
	help
	Say Y here if you have MTK_BMA253 touch panel BMA253_LOWPASS.

	If unsure, say N.

	To compile this dirver as a module, choose M here: the
	module will be called.

